# 429 Rate Limit Response Example

HTTP/1.1 429 Too Many Requests
Content-Type: application/arky.error+json
RateLimit-Limit: 600
RateLimit-Remaining: 0
RateLimit-Reset: 60
Retry-After: 60

{
  "@type": "ARKY:ErrorEnvelope@v1",
  "code": "wire.rate_limited",
  "severity": "transient",
  "detail": "Rate limit exceeded: 600 requests per 10 minutes",
  "retry": { "allowed": true, "after": "PT60S" }
}
